 NB: Methodology, Supervision, Validation, Writing &#8211; review &amp; editing. IT: Supervision, Validation, Visualization, Writing &#8211; review &amp; editing.</p><p>The corrected Acknowledgements section reads as follows:</p></sec></body><back><ack><p>We are grateful to the colleagues Myriam A. Koudjoue, Christophe Iwaka, Youssouf Toukourou, and Eloi Attakpa for comments on an earlier version of this manuscript. We also thank the reviewers for comments on an earlier version of this manuscript. AA was supported by African Research Initiative for Scientific Excellence (ARISE).</p><p>The publisher apologizes for this mistake. The original version of this article has been updated.</p></ack></back></article></pmc-articleset>